title: Tommy Trash - Trashed 010 (Split Tracks)
description:
Had some free time so I decided to split the tracks of Trashed Radio. This was released on 2013-10-21. If you really like it, I recommend subscribing to his podcast.

Thanks to 1001tracklists.com for providing me with the tracklist and Tommy Trash for making it incredibly difficult to figure out the correct timings in splitting these tracks.

enjoy
